Name: Hidden Histories: The Principality
About the game: Over sixty hidden object scenes to master - Themed images in each scene. Based on a fictional Principality in the Pyrenees. In each scene the player must find items from a list that are hidden within the scene's main picture. Six hints available per scene with no cooldown period.
